description: You can instantly tell that this culinary crew is “serious about ‘que” when you see that massive grill. You just know that the succulent meat that’s smokin’ inside is no joke. You’ll be serious about ‘que too once you take a bite of their mouth-watering selection: including Fruit Wood Smoked Baby Back Ribs, juicy Pulled Pork, and flavorful blazed Brisket. Their classic sides comprise Creamy Coleslaw, Snortz BBQ Beans, and more. When it comes to delicious BBQ, be sure not to sell yourself short - instead, head on down to Snortz. You'll be seriously satisfied.
name: Snortz Barbeque
